♪ Off to see the world

1815
01:45:59,686 --> 01:46:03,523
♪ There's such a lot of world

1816
01:46:03,607 --> 01:46:06,526
♪ To see

1817
01:46:07,444 --> 01:46:11,531
♪ We're after

1818
